<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        background: black;
        color: white;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      }

      /* MENU (exact index match) */
      .menu {
        position: fixed;
        top: 18px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        z-index: 20;

        display: flex;
        gap: 28px;

        font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
                     "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;

        font-size: 16px;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        text-transform: uppercase;

        color: rgba(240,240,240,0.78);
        mix-blend-mode: difference;

        pointer-events: auto;
      }

      .menu a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
        opacity: 0.85;
        transition: opacity 200ms ease, transform 200ms ease;
      }

      .menu a:hover {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .menu a.active {
        opacity: 1;
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-underline-offset: 4px;
      }

      /* TOP VIGNETTE (unchanged) */
      .menu-vignette {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 140px;
        z-index: 15;
        pointer-events: none;

        background: radial-gradient(
          ellipse at top center,
          rgba(0,0,0,0.70) 0%,
          rgba(0,0,0,0.45) 35%,
          rgba(0,0,0,0.18) 60%,
          rgba(0,0,0,0.00) 100%
        );

        -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(
          to bottom,
          rgba(0,0,0,1) 0%,
          rgba(0,0,0,1) 50%,
          rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%
        );

        mask-image: linear-gradient(
          to bottom,
          rgba(0,0,0,1) 0%,
          rgba(0,0,0,1) 50%,
          rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%
        );
      }

      /* =====================================================
         UPDATED: SOFTER + WIDER CONTENT VIGNETTE
         ===================================================== */
      .content-vignette {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;

        width: 88vw;   /* slightly wider = smoother transition into image */
        height: 100vh;

        z-index: 2;
        pointer-events: none;

        background: linear-gradient(
          to right,

          rgba(0,0,0,0.78) 0%,
          rgba(0,0,0,0.68) 35%,
          rgba(0,0,0,0.52) 55%,
          rgba(0,0,0,0.32) 72%,
          rgba(0,0,0,0.14) 88%,
          rgba(0,0,0,0.00) 100%
        );
      }

      /* LAYOUT */
      .layout {
        display: flex;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .content {
        width: 65vw;
        padding: 90px 60px 60px 60px;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 3;
      }

      .block {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
        opacity: 0.9;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .block a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-underline-offset: 3px;
      }

      /* RIGHT IMAGE */
      .bg {
        position: fixed;
        top: 40px;
        right: 100px;

        width: 705px;
        height: 620px;

        background-image: url("/mess_detail.png");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;

        opacity: 0.9;
        z-index: 1;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>

    <div class="menu-vignette"></div>

    <div class="menu">
      <a class="active" href="/about">About</a>
      <a href="/folded-map">Folded&nbsp;Map</a>
      <a href="/media">Media</a>
      <a href="/research">Research</a>
    </div>

    <div class="content-vignette"></div>

    <div class="layout">

      <div class="content">

      <div class="block">
          Hi, I'm Andrew Hallock.
        </div>

        <div class="block">
          This website brings together my work as a musician and researcher, spanning performance, composition, and interdisciplinary study. It serves as a space where artistic practice and inquiry meet, and where ongoing projects are made publicly accessible.
        </div>

        <div class="block">
          I am currently a doctoral candidate in the DocArtes program at the Orpheus Institute in Ghent, where my research explores connections between musical thought, historical material, and broader historical systems of representation and meaning.
        </div>

        <div class="block">
          Here you will find fragments of this work in different forms: texts, recordings, reflections, and evolving research materials. The site is not organized as a fixed archive, but as a working environment that develops over time.
        </div>

        <div class="block">
          For a more detailed overview of my background and work, a <a href="/cv-andrew-hallock.pdf" target="_blank">CV</a> is available here.
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="bg"></div>

    </div>

  </body>
</html>